OL,3,CDrugs found almost 900 times at prison
OL,4,Cin a year before 'worrying' inspection
OL,6,FMore than half of prisoners at the
OL,7,Ftroubled Parc Prison told inspectors
OL,8,Fit was easy to access drugs, while
OL,9,Fjust over a third at two of the main
OL,10,Fwings said they had developed a drug
OL,11,For alcohol problem since arriving at
OL,12,Fthe jail.
OL,14,FThat's according to the findings of an
OL,15,Finspection in January, which revealed
OL,16,Fthat almost 900 drugs finds were made
OL,17,Fin the year before the Bridgend prison
OL,18,Fwas inspected.
