OL,6,FThe prison has come under increased
OL,7,Fscrutiny in recent years, with 17
OL,8,Finmates having died at HMP Parc in
OL,9,F2024 ` more than at any other prison
OL,10,Fthat year.
OL,12,FThe inspection found that levels of
OL,13,Fviolence remained high, which
OL,14,Fprisoners attributed to "frustration
OL,15,Fwith a lack of consistency in the
OL,16,Fdaily regime, boredom, long periods
OL,17,Flocked up, the widespread availability
OL,18,Fof drugs and not having enough to eat".
