OL,4,Cin a year before 'worrying' inspection
OL,6,FThe report also found that levels of
OL,7,Fself-harm remained high and had
OL,8,Fincreased by 58% since the last
OL,9,Finspection.
OL,11,FHowever, it noted that since the
OL,12,Farrival of a new director in June
OL,13,F2024, the recruitment, retention and
OL,14,Fmorale of officers had improved, and
OL,15,Fwhile "far too many drugs were still
OL,16,Fgetting into the prison", "it was
OL,17,Fclear that Parc had begun to recover".
