OL,6,FG4S, which runs Parc, said it is
OL,7,F"working tirelessly on a comprehensive
OL,8,Fimprovement plan to once again deliver
OL,9,Fexcellent services at HMP Parc".
OL,11,FThe HM Inspectorate of Prisons report
OL,12,Fsaid the transition to a new
OL,13,Fmanagement contract at the prison was
OL,14,Fat the root of many of its problems,
OL,15,Fat a time when its former director had
OL,16,Fleft along with other senior leaders.
OL,17,FThe report said: "This had
OL,18,Ffundamentally destabilised the prison
OL,19,Fand left it unable to grip the
OL,20,Fproblems it faced."
