OL,6,FThe report said: "The new director
OL,7,Farrived in June 2024 and since then
OL,8,Fhad set about resetting the jail. He
OL,9,Fhad stabilised the leadership team,
OL,10,Fand improved the recruitment,
OL,11,Fretention and morale of officers. At
OL,12,Fthe time of our inspection, there had
OL,13,Fbeen no more drug-related or self-
OL,14,Finflicted deaths since his arrival.
