OL,6,F"He and his team were in no doubt
OL,7,Fabout the challenges that they faced.
OL,8,FThe prison had become far too violent;
OL,9,Flevels of self-harm (already too high
OL,10,Fat our last inspection) had increased
OL,11,Fby 60%. Despite the impressive
OL,12,Fcommitment of the security team, which
OL,13,Fhad made nearly 900 drugs finds in the
OL,14,Flast year, there were far too many
OL,15,Fdrugs getting into the jail."
