OL,6,FChief Inspector Charlie Taylor, of HM
OL,7,FInspectorate of Prisons, said: "The
OL,8,Fstaff team, which was used to being
OL,9,Fproud of the place at which they
OL,10,Fworked, had been through a very
OL,11,Fdifficult time, but there were signs
OL,12,Fthat things were beginning to turn
OL,13,Faround. "Partnership working between
OL,14,Fprison leaders and the new education
OL,15,Fprovider had begun to improve, as had
OL,16,Fthe regime and practical release
OL,17,Fplanning arrangements.
